title: Key Matchups in the Conference Championships | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We dive deep into each of the two games this weekend while highlighting the players to bet on and avoid. Then we build our daily fantasy lineup for the conference championships.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
